\v 8 ThenВҰ312764 I'llВҰ312764 makeВҰ312764 that cityВҰ312767 into a wastelandВҰ312769 \add вүҲthat's something to scoff at\add*вҖ”everyoneВҰ312771 who passesВҰ312772 by will be appalledВҰ312774 andВҰ312764 will \add вүҲmock it because of all itsВҰ312780 disasters\add*.
