\v 3 The next dayВҰ312987, when \add вүҲPashhur\add* released Yirmeyah from the stocksВҰ312995, Yirmeyah saidВҰ312996 to him, вҖңYahwehВҰ313002 won'tВҰ312999 call you вҖҳPashhurвҖҷ, butВҰ312986 вҖҳMagorВҰ313007-MissabibвҖҷ \add (which means вҖҳsurrounded by terrorвҖҷ)\add*,
