\v 5 I'llВҰ313043 give away all the wealthВҰ313048 of this cityВҰ313049вҖ”all its products and valuables, and all the treasuresВҰ313064 of Yehudah'sВҰ313066 kingsВҰ313065вҖ”to their enemiesВҰ313069. They'llВҰ313067 plunderВҰ313070 it, seize it, and carry it off to BabylonВҰ313073.
\v 6 ThenВҰ313075 you, PashhurВҰ313076 will \add вүҲbe taken\add* into captivityВҰ313081 \add вүҲalong with all the others in your home\add*. You'll \add вүҲbe taken\add* to BabylonВҰ313082, and you'll dieВҰ313085 there and be buriedВҰ313087вҖ”you and all your friendsВҰ313091 who you've prophesiedВҰ313094 these lies to.
